*2018年8月15日左岸地下电站首台机组（6号机组）浇筑封顶<ref>{{cite web |title=乌东德左岸地下电站首台机组浇筑封顶 |url=https://www.chinanews.com/ny/2018/08-17/8603541.shtml |website=中国新闻网 |accessdate=2021-03-30 |archive-date=2019-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190225092733/http://www.chinanews.com/ny/2018/08-17/8603541.shtml }}</ref>
